<DocsPageTitle Path="Extensions/SVG Chart Zoom and Pan">
    Blazorise SVG Chart Zoom and Pan
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageLead>
    Zoom and pan native SVG charts with declarative options and event callbacks.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    SVG chart zoom can be enabled declaratively with <Code>SvgChartZoom</Code> or configured through <Code>SvgChartOptions.Zoom</Code>. Use <Code>ViewportChanged</Code>, <Code>Zoomed</Code>, and <Code>Panned</Code> to track viewport changes.
</DocsPageParagraph>

<DocsPageSubtitle>
    Examples
</DocsPageSubtitle>

<DocsPageSection>
    <DocsPageSectionHeader Title="Zoom and pan">
        Wheel over the chart to zoom, and drag the plot area to pan.
    </DocsPageSectionHeader>
